data.description: You will love the floor plan of this spacious 3 bedroom, 2 full bath, with second living room or office upstairs. Bedrooms are split with 2 bedrooms, full bath, and utility room in one wing and the primary bedroom in the back of the house. Have fun entertaining in the large living room dining room area.  Enjoy a morning cup of coffee or an evening beverage on the extended back patio with arbor that can be entered from the living room, primary bedroom, or kitchen. The primary bedroom is very spacious and features a large walk in closet. The primary bathroom has dual vanities, garden tub, and separate shower. The eat-in kitchen is very has room for a large table and chairs. You'll find everything you want and need in this lovely home! Come take a look! This home is priced to sell!
